Team Dino Desperado proudly presents our 4K entry!


10 Jul 2018 21:55






Alt Title: Cowboys vs Dinosaurs

This is the most fun I've ever had writing an article, all thanks to my wonderful co-authors Papa Sen. The inspiration came as I was thinking 'What is something 5-year-old me would enjoy?'

cowboys, of course!

Special thanks to Alces_alces for improving the journals far beyond what I could have possibly done alone.

Clickhappen!

-much.



~~Honorary Dino Desperados~~

djkaktus- for motivating me to get this done and offering critique. Sorry I couldn't get them to lasso a Brontosaurus, but it just wouldn't fit in the narrative. Believe me, I tried.

Ihp-for giving me a literal goldmine of information and encouraging me to write when this was barely a concept.

TSATPWTCOTTTADC- for helping me so much with the CSS used in the journals and helping find a better T-Rex picture!

JanitorCakeworth- for hearing endless stupid ideas and helping me with this from start to finish.

The Great Hippo for creating the template used in this article.
~~The Beautiful Critters~~
FilaYoung

Special thanks to everyone in the r/SCPDeclassified Discord for enduring my never-ending requests for crit; same to the fine folks in the Unspeakable One's SCP Discord server.

You're all great and this project could not have been accomplished without your help.
